caption:
It was the "I got you" that got us 🥲👇🏾⁠
⁠
"I’ve been dealing with depression, and my amazing wife secretly arranged for my big brother to fly from Houston to Los Angeles to surprise me.⁠
⁠
When l saw him, I was overwhelmed with gratitude and love. My siblings are my best friends, and their support means the world to me.⁠
⁠
If you’re struggling with mental health, remember you’re not alone. Reach out to your loved ones—they can make a huge difference. Stay strong and take care of yourselves." - @carloschopkins⁠
